description:
Choose one of three unique heroes and go to exciting levels filled with a variety of enemies - from ordinary ordinary soldiers to huge and difficult bosses! To defeat enemies, the player is given a wide arsenal of weapons, which can be unlocked and upgraded as the game progresses. Defeat enemies, earn gold and upgrade your guns!

Each level presents a new challenge, requiring the player's tactical thinking, reaction and skill. With each victory, the player gets the opportunity to improve his character and expand his arsenal of weapons, which helps him cope with more difficult challenges.

Immerse yourself in exciting gameplay, dynamic combat and unforgettable enemy battles, making each playthrough a unique and exciting adventure!

GAME FEATURES:
• Top-down shooter genre for those who like to test their accuracy and reaction;
• Many levels with varying difficulty and a variety of enemies;
• Dynamic and fun gameplay that doesn’t let you get bored;
